snippet.textDisplay:
I had never heard of Amjad Sabri Saab before this I listened to the song. But then it hit me like a brick and fell in love with the song.

This song is now so special to me. Very special. Will remember this song with his memories. But most importantly, it has reinforced the lesson into me that we will all die and all we have is the love and connection to other people. We must love others and work together without our ego interfering in between. We have to become selfless and appreciate the gifts of others. We must appreciate what other human beings have to offer us.

Hope everyone gets this. Just lose your goddamn egos and love other people unconditionally. Become selfless.
